07:00.880 --> 07:04.467
MAN: I alone was the only survivor.

07:06.719 --> 07:10.389
My entire robot army,
completely annihilated!

07:11.432 --> 07:17.980
In my dreams,
I still see arrows falling like rain.

07:18.356 --> 07:20.149
What does the tower hold

07:20.232 --> 07:22.777
that would make you sacrifice
a whole army?

07:23.361 --> 07:27.573
Treasure? Gold? Rubies?

07:27.657 --> 07:29.075
Bah!

07:29.158 --> 07:33.245
Nothing as materialistic as treasure.

07:33.871 --> 07:37.750
At the top of the tower
is a mystical well,

07:38.167 --> 07:41.504
the well of King Ozric.

07:42.546 --> 07:48.761
Those who reach the infamous well
are granted one wish,

07:49.637 --> 07:52.181
your greatest desire.

07:52.640 --> 07:54.642
Get out of the great khan's chair.

07:54.725 --> 07:56.727
What are you, telling stories again?

07:56.936 --> 08:00.773
Get swabbing the deck,
or I'll toss you overboard, you has-been.

08:01.357 --> 08:02.858
(WHEELS SQUEAKING)

08:12.702 --> 08:13.744
JACK: Excuse me.

08:14.120 --> 08:16.664
Is this place you speak of real?

08:16.747 --> 08:17.999
Of course.

08:18.124 --> 08:21.419
As a matter of fact, we're passing it now.

08:21.502 --> 08:22.628
There!

08:23.838 --> 08:25.131
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

08:26.048 --> 08:29.677
In the center of that mist-shrouded isle

08:30.302 --> 08:34.598
lies the treasure of King Ozric.

08:36.350 --> 08:37.518
Thank you.

08:38.352 --> 08:39.520
Uh-huh.

08:40.104 --> 08:41.355
Oh, w-w-wait!

08:41.439 --> 08:44.108
I beg you, reconsider.

08:44.817 --> 08:49.739
There are only three archers,
yet they decimated my whole army.

08:49.822 --> 08:52.658
You are just one man.

08:52.950 --> 08:54.368
Do the math.

08:54.869 --> 08:56.370
Why attempt it?

08:58.706 --> 09:00.124
That well could get me home.

09:00.291 --> 09:02.835
There are other ways to get home.

09:04.170 --> 09:05.212
Not for me.

09:07.548 --> 09:09.759
