13:23.721 --> 13:25.472
(PANTING)

13:44.450 --> 13:45.868
(ARROWS WHOOSHING)

13:49.580 --> 13:51.206
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

14:37.461 --> 14:40.130
