14:44.009 --> 14:46.387
It's no use. No one can fight like this.

14:48.263 --> 14:54.603
A great warrior must be in tune
with all of his senses.

14:54.895 --> 14:59.775
Only then will you be able
to extend your awareness

15:00.150 --> 15:04.363
so that you may fight on any level.

15:05.072 --> 15:06.907
Try again.

15:06.990 --> 15:08.075
Yes, <i>sifu.</i>

15:09.827 --> 15:11.745
I must fight on their level.

15:11.829 --> 15:13.539
