19:22.954 --> 19:24.956
(RUSTLING)

19:51.650 --> 19:53.485
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

20:23.515 --> 20:25.475
(MAN GROANS)

20:26.601 --> 20:27.644
Where...

20:28.145 --> 20:29.229
W-what...

20:31.815 --> 20:32.983
I can see.

20:33.191 --> 20:34.443
We're restored.

20:34.693 --> 20:36.027
How is it possible?

20:36.111 --> 20:37.904
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS)

20:42.409 --> 20:44.286
You have broken our curse.

20:44.369 --> 20:45.620
We thank you.

20:49.291 --> 20:51.293
I have come to make a wish at this well.

20:51.752 --> 20:54.045
The well is yours.

20:57.716 --> 20:59.718
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS)

21:08.310 --> 21:13.064
VOICE: Proclaim your wish, great warrior,

21:14.107 --> 21:20.655
and it will be fulfilled
beyond your wildest dream.

21:23.575 --> 21:26.203
My quest has finally come to an end.

21:26.912 --> 21:28.121
