to reach this well.

21:41.384 --> 21:44.638
When we arrived, we stood before the well
and made our wish:

21:45.096 --> 21:47.015
To be the greatest of warriors.

21:47.224 --> 21:50.560
The spirit of the well
did indeed make us great warriors,

21:50.852 --> 21:54.689
but in so doing,
robbed us of our sight and our minds,

21:54.773 --> 21:57.234
